OL,6,FThe three-toed sloth is half blind,
OL,7,Fhalf deaf and one of the slowest
OL,8,Fanimals on earth.
OL,10,FNative to the rainforests in Central
OL,11,Fand South America, sloths are so slow
OL,12,Fthat vegetation, such as algae, can
OL,13,Fgrow on their backs.
OL,15,FFor some time now, the British economy
OL,16,Fhas been doing a passable impression
OL,17,Fof a sloth.
